node.text: Super soft, buoyant, lively— and yet tough as nails—all at the same time. Only Z-Man’s remarkable ElaZtech baits offer such fish-centric qualities. And when your target species slash and gash with serious incisors, you best arm yourself with a bait whose tail can take a pounding and come back ready for more. In pursuit of “doormat” sized fluke, flounder and other species, the @onthewatermagazine crew show you how to rig and fish Z-Man's ElaZtech DoormatadorZ—a Pro-Cure scented, 5" (NEW) & 6" grub. #doormatadorz #elaztech #10xTough #madeinusa #zmanfishing #onthewatermagazine #flukebait #curlytailgrub #flounderbait #jigging

node.text: The original ChatterBait pro, Bryan Thrift, breaks down his favorite bass lure yet, the Z-Man Big Blade ChatterBait. See what makes this powerful, vibe-inducing bladed jig tick and why Thrift believes the bait is destined to become the next ChatterBait sensation. Driven by a magnum engine of a ChatterBlade—more than twice the size and thump of a standard hex-blade—the Big Blade ChatterBait puts a virtual subwoofer at the end of your line, moving water and pulsing bass' lateral lines like no other lure to date. Following three years of R&D, Thrift has given his blessing on the definitive, head-banging bait and says it’s your turn to experience the Big Blade BOOM. @bryanthriftfishing #zmanfishing #bigbladechatterbait #bladedjig #bigblade #chatterbait #icast2021 #newproduct

node.text:
Free-swinging Texas Eye Finesse and Texas Eye TeXL jigheads by Z-Man let their luminous 3D eyes do the talking. Spawned from the original Texas Eye Jig, the the finesse and mega-sized technical jig designs produce visual eye candy and upgraded swimming action to any bait you choose.

The design goal of the Texas Eye was to build a fresh- and saltwater jig that married the snag immunity of a Texas rig with the frenetic bait movements of a free-swinging jighead. The new Texas Eye Finesse jig melds seamlessly with Ned-style and other finesse baits, while the TeXL jighead activates mongo swimbaits or other 5-inch-plus soft plastics.
#texaseyejigheads #texaseyefinesse #texaseyeTeXL #zmanfishing
@flatsclasstv

node.text:
Imagine an ultra-realistic swimbait that combines the malleability and vitality of the softest plastics with the durability of a hardbait. Give the swimbait highly detailed preyfish sculpting and a smartly-designed curved paddletail for lively subtle swim action with just a bit of a baitfish wobble.  Armed with a heavy duty 5/0 or 7/0 Mustad UltraPoint hook in 4” or 5” bait sizes, respectively, the HerculeZ presents the ideal match for monster fish with an attitude problem. The HerculeZ’ internal jighead is armed with a second, ventral eyelet for adding a belly treble hook. Swimbait profile features 3D eyes, ultra-detailed fins, gills and anatomy, each hand-painted in popular Z-Man color patterns.
These will hit the shelves in the Fall (2021). 
@flatsclasstv
#herculez #prerigged #swimbait #elaztech #zmanfishing #10xTough #tarponbait #bullredbait #snookbait #bigbassbait

node.text:
Designed by Z-Man pro and jig fishing ace @davidwalkerfishing , the CrossEyeZ ChatterBait leverages the weedless, oversized eye design of Z-Man’s CrossEyeZ jig series. A custom 5/0 O’Shaughnessy hook bolsters hookup and landing percentages. For optimal snag resistance around wood and grass, an adjustable, v-shaped, coated multi-strand wire weedguard deflects cover and prevents snagging and fouling, while folding back during hooksets. A dual trailer keeper, with molded lead and wire spikes, offers the ultimate in trailer security. Hand-tied silicone skirts are secured to the hook-shank with stainless wire for maximum longevity. Durable, color-matched jighead and hallmark ‘cross eyes’ add attraction. With a custom, super-hard stainless hex-shaped ChatterBlade and uniquely designed line tie snap that reduces fouling and enhances durability, the CrossEyeZ ChatterBait presents strong, bold vibration, unmatched durability and superior snag resistance.
Available in ten colors and 3/8-, ½- and ¾-ounce sizes.
#crosseyezchatterbait #chatterbait #zmanfishing #snagresistant #bladedjig

node.text: In part 7 of our behind-the-scenes GOAT ToadZ series, we reveal more tweaks in our prototype bait molds before going out on the water with Z-Man pros. Miles “Sonar” Burghoff offers his initial impressions as well as a few cool rigging tips. Meanwhile, Brian “B-Lat” Latimer hits up a local pond and breaks the bait down to its finest details. Take watch and a listen to the bait’s action and sound, and once again, let us know what you think of the GOAT ToadZ’ metamorphosis. #goattoadz #elaztech #10xTough #topwater #madeinusa #zmanfishing @sonarfishing @brian_latimer @zmanfishingproducts

node.text:
Parading a pair of flattened, mega-sized flapper claws, the new 3.75-inch Hella CrawZ is a compact crawfish-profile jig trailer and flipping bait with bonus tricks under its crown. The bait’s appeal lies within its 10X Tough ElaZtech composition. At rest, the Hella CrawZ’ buoyant pincers float up and hover in full menace mode. The slightest twitch of the line or faintest underwater flow activate its claws—and when you speed-reel it, watch the claws flap and vibrate like mad.
*Available at outdoor retailers in September (2021)
#HellaCrawZ #elaztech #10xTough #madeinusa #zmanfishing #flippingbait #jigtrailer #crawfishbait @markdanielsjr

node.text: Super soft, buoyant, lively— and yet tough as nails—all at the same time. Only Z-Man’s remarkable ElaZtech baits offer such fish-centric qualities. And when your target species slash and gash with serious incisors, you best arm yourself with a bait whose tail can take a pounding and come back ready for more. In pursuit of “doormat” sized fluke, flounder and other species, the @onthewatermagazine crew show you how to rig and fish Z-Man's ElaZtech DoormatadorZ—a Pro-Cure scented, 5" (NEW) & 6" grub. #doormatadorz #elaztech #10xTough #madeinusa #zmanfishing #onthewatermagazine #flukebait #curlytailgrub #flounderbait #jigging
